"Hello all homeschooling Moms and Dads! I am just advertising myself.
I work as an Indenpendent Beauty Consultant for Mary Kay."

This list is not designed for advertising your business. This is a
list for discussing unschooling. I'm sorry that got through
everyone....back to your regular unschooling discussion.

Ren

From: mommajj02
To: unschoolingbasics@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Sunday, February 27, 2005 9:44 PM
Subject: [unschoolingbasics] Just working here



Hello all homeschooling Moms and Dads! I am just advertising myself.
I work as an Indenpendent Beauty Consultant for Mary Kay. I love my
job because I get to work from home, but because I am just starting
out (3 months) I can always use more customers! Not only do we just
sell great products we also offer parties. There are many types but
the most common is the facial party. You get to try all of our great
skin care products right in you own home. And its all for free. For
hosting a party you recieve a free gift and earn free products. The
way you earn free products is by the total you sell at the party is
the way I base the amonut. Just recentally at a party with only four
women the hostess earned $40.00 in free products. She earned an
additional $20.00 from outside orders from here work. We have
wonderful products that really work. I know I use them everyday. So
does my whole family now. Please e-mail me if you would like to host
a party or just have any questions. I do individual consults too. You
can try dozens of samples and its all free. The only you pay for is
the products if any you choose to buy. And just because you all have
helped me so much in homeschooling my daughter you can all recieve
10% off anything and everything you order. Please tell anyone you
know too. Its a real big help. Its so hard to get my name out there
but hopefully this will help. Thanks so much for your time

Jessica
Independent Beauty Consultant
